    <item>
      <title>拜登竞选团队 6 月份筹集的资金已消耗 93%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/biden-s-campaign-burned-through-93-of-money-it-raised-in-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登的竞选团队陷入困境，进入 7 月份时，拜登手头只有 9600 万美元现金。上个月，拜登的竞选团队疯狂支出，耗费了 6 月份筹集资金的约 93%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/biden-s-campaign-burned-through-93-of-money-it-raised-in-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 15:03:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
